    "chunk_id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2003_Solutions_2003s_page_001_14",
    "text": "which is precisely (k) times the geometric mean of the terms on the left. Thus AM-GM shows that the terms under consideration on the left exceed those on the right; adding these inequalities over all k yields the desired result.",
